## Root Cause Analysis — Recurring Pattern

### RC-6: Stale Metrics Never Updated After Fix Cycles
Every fix cycle resolves spec issues but fails to update the 4 metric files (`00-overview.md`, `10-ai-handoff-readiness-report.md`, `99-consistency-report.md`, `14-spec-issues/00-overview.md`). This has happened in Fix Phases H, O, T, and now again after Phases 22–26.

**Prevention:** After ANY fix phase, immediately grep for the old count across ALL root-level files and update every occurrence.

### RC-7: "Fixed" Without Verification
Issues were reported as resolved without running grep to confirm the fix is present in the actual file. The `is_day_excluded`, IPC name mismatch, and orphaned commands were claimed fixed but remain in the source files.

**Prevention:** After claiming a fix, run `grep -rn "old_pattern"` to confirm zero remaining occurrences. If grep still finds the pattern, the fix is incomplete.

